(165, 39, 'mfn-page-items-seo', 'The review and marketing platform\n\n<h2 class=\"h2_reset h2_gray\">The review and marketing <br> platform that gets you found.</h2>\r\n<p>Collecting reviews and engaging with your customers on <br> Hellopeter\'s platform helps your business build trust, get <br> discovered and stand out in search results.</p>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfetures_page_top_sec\n\nGet Found\n\n<a href=\"#\"><img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/get-found.png\" alt=\"\" /></a>\r\n<p>Get found</p>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeature_topsec_colitem\n\nGet Found\n\n<a href=\"#\"><img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/build-trust.png\" alt=\"\" /></a>\r\n<p>Build Trust</p>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeature_topsec_colitem\n\nGet Found\n\n<a href=\"#\"><img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/engage.png\" alt=\"\" /></a>\r\n<p>Engage</p>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeature_topsec_colitem\n\nGet Found\n\n<a href=\"#\"><img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/learn.png\" alt=\"\" /></a>\r\n<p>Measure & Learn</p>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeature_topsec_colitem\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/get-found-2.png\" alt=\"get-found\"/>\n\nright\n\n<h4 class=\"h4_white h4_reset\">Get a listing, get found</h4>\r\n<p>Become discoverable by featuring on South Africa\'s number 1 consumer review platform, and make your Google organic search results stand out with your Hellopeter business profile.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeature_Get_listing\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screenshot_2019-01-27-Business-Portal-Hellopeter-Features-1.png\" alt=\"Screenshot_2019-01-27 Business Portal Hellopeter - Features\"/>\n\ncenter\n\nYour Google presence\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/onsite-presence-icon.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<h6>Your Google presence</h6>\r\n<p>Hellopeter business profile pages claim top spot on Google search when searchers type \"(company name) reviews.\" Improve what searchers see by collecting reviews.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeture_getlist_bottom_item\n\nYour Google presence\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/rich-snippets-icon.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<h6>Google star ratings</h6>\r\n<p>Hellopeter business profile pages claim top spot on Google search when searchers type \"(company name) reviews.\" Improve what searchers see by collecting reviews.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeture_getlist_bottom_item\n\nYour Google presence\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/google-presence-icon.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<h6>Onsite presence</h6>\r\n<p>Hellopeter business profile pages claim top spot on Google search when searchers type \"(company name) reviews.\" Improve what searchers see by collecting reviews.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeture_getlist_bottom_item\n\nYour Google presence\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/top-business-icon.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<h6>Be a Top Business</h6>\r\n<p>Hellopeter business profile pages claim top spot on Google search when searchers type \"(company name) reviews.\" Improve what searchers see by collecting reviews.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeture_getlist_bottom_item\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ezgif.com-gif-maker-1.png\" alt=\"ezgif.com-gif-maker (1)\"/>\n\nright\n\nBuild a brand\n\n<h4 class=\"h4_gray h4_reset\">Build a brand that your customers trust</h4>\r\n<p>Let your customer reviews speak for your business. Collect more reviews and showcase them to increase customer confidence and boost sales.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBuild_brand_section_heading\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ezgif.com-gif-maker.png\" alt=\"ezgif.com-gif-maker\"/>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nCollect more reviews\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screenshot_2019-01-27-Business-Portal-Hellopeter-Features7.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"p_tag\">Collect more reviews</p>\r\n<p>Your customers are your best marketers! The Hellopeter review collection tools make it easy for your business to start scaling your customer testimonials.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBuild_brand_content_item\n\nCollect more reviews\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screenshot_2019-01-27-Business-Portal-Hellopeter-Features8.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"p_tag\">TrustIndex ratings and reviews</p>\r\n<p>Your customers are your best marketers! The Hellopeter review collection tools make it easy for your business to start scaling your customer testimonials.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBuild_brand_content_item\n\nCollect more reviews\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screenshot_2019-01-27-Business-Portal-Hellopeter-Features9.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"p_tag\">Social sharing</p>\r\n<p>Your customers are your best marketers! The Hellopeter review collection tools make it easy for your business to start scaling your customer testimonials.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBuild_brand_content_item\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/engage-icon-image.png\" alt=\"engage-icon-image\"/>\n\nright\n\n<h4 class=\"h4_white h4_reset\">Engage with your customers</h4>\r\n<p>Customer service matters. Do more than simply manage your reviews, connect with your customers and make every experience meaningful.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeature_Get_listing\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/engage-image.png\" alt=\"engage-image\"/>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nManage reviews\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/manage-reviews-icon.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<h6>Manage reviews</h6>\r\n<p>Use the Hellopeter business portal to get notified, access reviews, respond publicly and privately, and apply templated responses to ensure that your customers are heard.</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeture_getlist_bottom_item\n\nManage reviews\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/collect-nps-icon.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<h6>Collect and measure your NPS</h6>\r\n<p>No business has a perfect record. Negative sentiment is part of your business – learn from it and create lifetime customers by converting detractors into brand promoters.</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nfeture_getlist_bottom_item\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/data-inform-icon.png\" alt=\"data-inform-icon\"/>\n\nright\n\n<h4 class=\"h4_gray h4_reset\">Build a brand that your customers trust</h4>\r\n<p>Let your customer reviews speak for your business. Collect more reviews and showcase them to increase customer confidence and boost sales.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBuild_brand_section_heading\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/data-image.png\" alt=\"data-image\"/>\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/data-inform-dashboard.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"p_tag\">Dashboard</p>\r\n<p>Understand how your business is performing at a glance, identify trends and measure progress.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBuild_brand_content_item\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/data-inform-reporting.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"p_tag\">Reporting</p>\r\n<p>Get a handle of your review data and compare to other businesses in your industry.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBuild_brand_content_item\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/data-inform-onsite.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"p_tag\">Onsite & Google Analytics reporting</p>\r\n<p>Understand how people find your business, and how much traffic Google drives to your profile.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBuild_brand_content_item\n\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/data-inform-agent.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"p_tag\">Agent reporting</p>\r\n<p>For larger teams, understand how your agents perform and identify opportunities for improvement.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBuild_brand_content_item\n\nBecome a Hellopeter business\n\n<h2 class=\"h2_reset h2_white\">Become a Hellopeter business</h2>\r\n<a class=\"primary_btn a_firsrt_item\" href=\"#\">get started for free</a>\r\n<a class=\"primary_btn a_second_item\" href=\"#\">view our pacgage</a>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBecome_Hellopeter\n\n'),
