(236, 84, 'mfn-page-items-seo', 'Top Section\n\n<h2 class=\"h2_white h2_reset\">Let your customers do<br>\r\nyour marketing for you.</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p_white display_block \">Collect and use reviews to build trust, get found<br>\r\nand increase sales.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p_white display_none\">Collect and use reviews to build trust, get found and increase sales.</p>\r\n<a class=\" primary_btn a_bg_primary\" href=\"#\">FIND THE PACKAGE FOR ME</a>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nhomepage_top_sec\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brand2.png\" alt=\"brand2\"/>\n\ncenter\n\npayment_brand_column\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brand3.png\" alt=\"brand3\"/>\n\ncenter\n\npayment_brand_column\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brand4.png\" alt=\"brand4\"/>\n\ncenter\n\npayment_brand_column\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brand5.png\" alt=\"brand5\"/>\n\ncenter\n\npayment_brand_column\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brand6.png\" alt=\"brand6\"/>\n\ncenter\n\npayment_brand_column\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brand1.png\" alt=\"brand1\"/>\n\ncenter\n\npayment_brand_column\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/trusted-brand-mockup.png\" alt=\"trusted-brand-mockup\"/>\n\ntrusted_brand_lcolumn\n\nBuild a trusted brand\n\n<h2 class=\"h2_reset\" >Build a trusted brand</h2>\r\n<p>Reviews create content that improves your Google search results, making your business more visible, and easier for consumers to find you. Use your Hellopeter business account to collect reviews and engage with your customers, and control what consumers see in Google and on South Africa\'s largest review platform.</p>\r\n<a class=\"primary_btn a_bg_primary\" href=\"#\">Learn More</a>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\ntrusted_brand_rcolumn\n\n<h2 class=\"h2_reset h2_white\">Display credibility and increase sales</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p_white\">Amplify your exposure across Google organic search, social media and Hellopeter channels by showcasing your top reviews, TrustIndex and other Hellopeter marketing widgets.</p>\r\n<a class=\"primary_btn a_bg_white\" href=\"#\">Learn More</a>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\ntrusted_brand_rcolumn\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/increase-sales-mockup.png\" alt=\"increase-sales-mockup\"/>\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/customer-experience-mockup2.png\" alt=\"customer-experience-mockup2\"/>\n\ntrusted_brand_lcolumn\n\nBuild a trusted brand\n\n<h2 class=\"h2_reset\" >Create great customer experiences</h2>\r\n<p>Customer service matters, so do more than simply manage your reviews. Connect with customers on an independent website consumers trust, and make every experience meaningful.</p>\r\n<a class=\"primary_btn a_bg_primary\" href=\"#\">Learn More</a>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\ntrusted_brand_rcolumn\n\n<h2 class=\"h2_reset \">Let your data inform you</h2>\r\n<p class=\"\">Your customer reviews are full of rich data. This is a great opportunity to gain insights about your products and services, identify trends, measure progress and make informed decisions.</p>\r\n<a class=\"primary_btn a_bg_primary\" href=\"#\">Learn More</a>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\ntrusted_brand_rcolumn\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wpbetheme/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/data-mockup2.png\" alt=\"data-mockup2\"/>\n\nLet_your_rdata\n\nBecome a Hellopeter business\n\n<h2 class=\"h2_reset h2_white\">Become a Hellopeter business</h2>\r\n<a class=\"primary_btn a_firsrt_item\" href=\"#\">get started for free</a>\r\n<a class=\"primary_btn a_second_item\" href=\"#\">view our pacgage</a>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nBecome_Hellopeter\n\n[bf id=\"212\"]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n[bf_user_posts_list id=\"212\"]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n'),
